# Photo-resistor

![../60-Meta-Attachments/40815a53e8ea96857e8e7ed31538fe3d.png|300](data:image/png;base64,)

> [!word] Light-dependent resistor (LDR)
>
> - A common type of [[61-Archive/20220311121416-light-sensor|Light Sensor]]
> - made of high resistance [[61-Archive/20220225130808-semiconductor|semiconductor]] material called **cadmium sulfide cells (Cds)**
> - highly sensitive to visible and near-infrared light
> - changes its **electrical resistance**
>   - from several thousand Ohms in the dark
>   - to only a hew hundred Ohms when light falls upon it.
